---
description: Reply language and package manager for this project
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

Always respond in English when chatting or editing in this project.

When running package manager commands (install, add, remove, run, build, dev, etc.), use `bun` instead of `npm`. For example: `bun install`, `bun add <package>`, `bun run dev`, `bun run build`.
